// DAL errors \uc0\u8594  mapped, unknown \u8594  INTERNAL_ERROR\
async function actionHandler<T>(fn: () => Promise<T>): Promise<ActionResult<T>>\
\
// Route Handler wrapper \'97 maps errors to HTTP status codes (401/403/404/409/422/500)\
async function routeHandler(fn: () => Promise<NextResponse>): Promise<NextResponse>\
\
function apiSuccess<T>(data: T, status = 200): NextResponse<\{ success: true; data: T \}>\
function apiError(message, status, code?): NextResponse<\{ success: false; error: string; code? \}>\
```\
