## COMPONENTS\
\
### `DashboardShell` (`"use client"`)\
Props: `\{ children, title: string, role?: TenantRole, userName?: string \}`\
- Sidebar nav filtered by `canSee(role, minRole)` using `ROLE_ORDER: \{operator:1, admin:2, master:3\}`\
- Nav items: `/dashboard`, `/card-types` (operator+), `/cards` (operator+), `/members` (master)\
- Settings link always shown; Logout: `authClient.signOut()` \uc0\u8594  `window.location.href = "/login"`\
- Active detection: `/dashboard` exact match; others `pathname.startsWith(href)`\
\
### `CardTypeWizard` (`"use client"`)\
Wraps `useCardTypeWizard(initialData?)`. On `submit()` success \uc0\u8594  `router.push(/card-types/$\{cardTypeId\})`.\
\
### `FieldTypeSelector` (`"use client"`)\
Props: `\{ value: FieldType|null, onChange?: (type: FieldType)=>void, readOnly?: boolean \}`\
- `onChange` is **optional** \'97 safe to render from Server Components without passing it\
- `readOnly=true` \uc0\u8594  buttons disabled, onClick is no-op\
\
### `CardActions` (`"use client"`)\
Props: `\{ cardId: string, actions: ActionDefinitionWithField[], onActionExecuted?: ()=>void \}`\
- Calls `executeActionAction(\{cardId, actionDefinitionId\})`\
- Shows before\uc0\u8594 after via `feedback.result.previousValue`/`newValue`\
- One action loading at a time (`loadingId` state)\
\
### `DynamicFieldRenderer` (`"use client"`)\
Props: `\{ fieldType: FieldType, value: unknown, label?: string \}`\
Switch \uc0\u8594  `TextRenderer|NumberRenderer|BooleanRenderer|DateRenderer|PhotoRenderer|SelectRenderer`\
\
### `DynamicFieldInput` (`"use client"`)\
Props: `\{ field: FieldDefinitionShape, value: unknown, onChange: (v)=>void, error?, disabled?, tenantId? \}`\
Switch \uc0\u8594  `TextInput|NumberInput|BooleanInput|DateInput|PhotoInput|SelectInput`\
- `PhotoInput` receives `tenantId` for upload\
- `SelectInput` receives `validationRules` to extract options\
\
### `ScanClient` (`"use client"`)\
Reads `scanMode` prop from server. `QRScanner` loaded with `dynamic(..., \{ssr:false\})`. Both hooks active simultaneously when mode is `"both"`. On scan \uc0\u8594  `router.push(/cards/$\{encodeURIComponent(code.trim())\})`.\
