## PATTERNS & CONVENTIONS\
\
**Imports**: `@/` alias for `src/`. Barrel exports in `src/lib/api/index.ts` and `src/lib/dal/index.ts`.\
\
**Error handling (Server Actions)**:\
```typescript\
// Pattern used in every page:\
try \{ context = await requireMaster() \}\
catch (e) \{\
  if (e instanceof AuthenticationError) redirect("/login")\
  if (e instanceof AuthorizationError) redirect("/dashboard") // or /card-types/[id]\
  redirect("/login")\
\}\
```\
\
**Server Components**: All pages are `async` server components with `export const dynamic = "force-dynamic"`. No ISR.\
\
**Client boundary split**: Heavy pages use `page.tsx` (server, auth+data) + `*Client.tsx` (client, UI state). Example: `cards/new/page.tsx` + `CardNewClient.tsx`.\
\
**Soft deletes**: `isActive = false` everywhere. DAL functions filter `isActive = true` by default.\
\
**Field value storage**: Type-specific columns (`value_text|number|boolean|date|json`). `mapValueToColumn` / `extractValue` in `field-values.ts` handle the mapping.\
\
**Form validation timing**: `useCardForm.validate()` called on submit only; per-field errors cleared on `setValue`.\
\
